creator: Bonju LTD
descriptionHtml:
Need a Ride? Introducing Bonju Ride! The newest Cab App in town.
Our services are sufficient and affordable for the public. Download the Bonju ride application and have a Bonju driver pick you up within minutes. Need a ride for later we have you sorted with the pre-ordering feature.

ON-DEMAND has never been so flexible, benefit from our wallet features, the modest prices, and a brilliant customer experience.

Hop on board a Bonju cab and get to your destination with a hefty smile!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Improved the UI during a trip.
- Promo Codes provide more feedback if there is an error.
- Cancellation screen now provides feedback functionality to call driver or dispatch according to certain issues.
- Can remove saved locations from the profile menu
- Added more information about the vehicle types before a user book.
- tapping a vehicle type will automatically move the selection to the centre of the screen.
- Performance improvements.
- Stability improvements.

creator: Bonju LTD
descriptionHtml:
Introducing Bonju Needs! The brand new all-in-one App aimed to cater for all your needs and make your life easier! Formally known as Bonju Needs, through our new brand and App update, we have introduced a number of NEW services related to Cabs and Delivery!

Through our app you you can now

- Ride Pool
- Book standard cabs
- Book cabs charged at hour rates
- Deliver parcels of ANY size
- Hire delivery runners

... and much more coming soon!
